Deploying a simple web application into Tomcat webserver using Bamboon Deploy Tomcat Application Task

1. Build a simple web application and create a WAR file
2. Install Tomcat webserver and configure Manager users for deploymentin conf/tomcat-users.xml
3. create a Bamboo Build plan to checkout the code and build to generate a WAR file
4. Create a deployment project that deploys the WAR file to the Tomcat application

